  <div class="modal-content">
    <span id="forgotClose" class="close">&times;</span>
    <h3 style="margin:0 0 10px 0;">Reset your password</h3>
    <p style="margin:0 0 12px 0;font-size:14px;">
      Enter your <strong>email</strong> or <strong>username</strong>. If an account exists, weâ€™ll send a reset link.
